To finalise: add the full CC-BY-4.0 text as LICENSE-DATA and the full Apache-2.0 text as
LICENSE-CODE (GitHub will then display both). This dual structure forces attribution on the
data (which is what makes the register citable) while keeping the tooling permissively reusable.
